<title>USA: Avant! says executives pleaded not guilty.</title>
<headline>Avant! says executives pleaded not guilty.</headline>
<dateline>SAN JOSE, Calif. 1997-04-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Top executives at Avant! Corp pleaded not guilty on Friday to charges they helped steal technology from rival Cadence Design Systems Inc, an Avant! spokesman said.</p>
<p>&quot;They're already back at work,&quot; John Huyett, a spokesman for Avant!, said after the arraignment in municipal court in San Jose. &quot;It's business as usual.&quot;</p>
<p>Earlier this week, the Santa Clara County, Calif., district attorney's office said it filed felony charges of conspiracy and theft of trade secrets against Avant!, its president and director Gerald Hsu, and other officials.</p>
